---
<div class="boot" id="boot">
  <pre class="out-line text-mute">[boot] cold start ok · loading identity matrix...</pre>
  <pre class="out-line text-mute">[boot] mounting <span class="text-accent">/dev/curiosity</span> on <span class="text-text">/home</span> ... <span class="text-ok">ok</span></pre>
  <pre class="out-line text-mute">[boot] starting <span class="text-accent">claude-code-style</span> shell ... <span class="text-ok">ok</span></pre>

  <section class="flex flex-wrap items-end gap-x-7 gap-y-3 my-4 pb-4 border-b border-dashed border-border">
    <h1 class="hero-name"><span class="slash">/</span>nullkey<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
    <div class="flex-1 min-w-[240px] text-[12px] text-dim">
      <div class="flex gap-2 py-[2px]"><span class="text-accent w-20">handle</span><span class="text-text">nullkey</span> <span class="text-mute">// 空键</span></div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 py-[2px]"><span class="text-accent w-20">role</span><span class="text-text">software engineer</span></div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 py-[2px]"><span class="text-accent w-20">focus</span><span class="text-text">backend · ai infra · llm tools</span></div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 py-[2px]"><span class="text-accent w-20">based</span><span class="text-text">shanghai</span></div>
      <p class="hero-tagline">building <em class="text-accent">quiet tools</em> for loud problems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p class="text-[12px] text-mute mb-4">
    type <span class="text-accent">help</span> for commands ·
    <span class="kbd">↑</span> <span class="kbd">↓</span> history ·
    <span class="kbd">Tab</span> autocomplete ·
    <span class="kbd">Ctrl</span>+<span class="kbd">L</span> clear
  </p>
</div>
